<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />
    <link href="..\lib\bootstrap\dist\css\bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>Index</title>
    <style>
        .bg {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: hsla(0, 100%, 90%, 0.3);
        }

        #login {
            position: absolute;
            top: 15vh;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px 0px #000;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container-fluid justify-content-center">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-4">
            </div>
            <div class="col-4" id="login">
                <h3 style="text-align:center">Login</h3>                
                <form asp-action="Index" asp-controller="Login" method="post">
                    <div class="form-group col">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Enter your Nick" name="NickName" />
                        <small style="text-align:left" id="NickName" class="form-text text-muted">NickName is Admin</small>
                        
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group col">
                        <input type="password" class="form-control" placeholder="Enter Your Password" name="Password" />
                        <small style="text-align:left" id="Password" class="form-text text-muted">Password is Password</small>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group col">
                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-danger btn-block">Login</button>                        
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
            <div class="col-4"></div>
        </div>     
    </div>
    <p>Please be aware that i didn't implement a registeration system.So there is only login :-). To be able to login Fill the Nickname part with "Admin" and Password part with "Password".</p>
</body>
</html>
